{"tid":1437430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班濕鳩泛民打手仲諗住喺連登吹奏劉細良？","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:11:49.000Z","uid":174295,"like":18,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5a4bec35513178a868c3131f7c15354791b714","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=r_EhQw1j5o0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr_EhQw1j5o0&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=7b69fee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=r_EhQw1j5o0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地都講到明要同班勇武徹底切割，你班人仲對依條分化撚有任何期望？大家唔記得左左膠以前點樣迫害我地？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要阻止左膠中共全面滲透依次運動，就要同依啲分化三毛割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca56f6c97a486fc22eda3f4ad6b66500685198c4","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"全面狙擊左膠三毛劉細良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3838c6063a1d40640fe287e141c22b05be16e6","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"cb4d8374142801afd0a81294bf28ce59de3be35b","tid":1437430,"uid":73924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2fef49055a71578cc037c917f2aa4573d4e605","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:01:48.000Z","msg":"要場運動成功，就要全面同所有左膠泛民割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0db00977b4c192df52a5a36bbdc6f9f8072e2cc","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母劉細良 諗住收割抗爭成果</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec3e46ec5361df0e25553c5b508d301bfd014207","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該唔好造神啦 有返啲獨立思考啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"e063acd8eda92107bd3cc02792ae039654100aea","tid":1437430,"uid":73924,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"慎防左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b382d70e8c5f71858ee70ee511438b9b0e0053","tid":1437430,"uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>販民左膠共諜偽抗爭賣港實錄</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<em>第十一次更新</em><br />\n<br />\n69 #劉小麗、#姚松炎 於facebook上割勇武蓆<br />\n616 #林卓廷 指我地贏緊 5:0 有義士唔同意就同糾察逼義士除口罩<br />\n617 #朱凱廸 叫人小組討論<br />\n617 #民陣 民陣義務律師團隊發聲明同伍展邦義務律師行割蓆，人格謀殺伍律師<br />\n621 #張超雄 護送狗車入狗竇<br />\n621 #黃之鋒 於警察總部門口搞大台投票決定聚散<br />\n626 #林朗彥 G20日本登報亂咁?又唔道歉<br />\n71 #梁耀忠、#林卓廷、#毛孟靜、#鄺俊宇、#區諾軒、#張超雄、#毛孟靜 恐嚇及阻止市民行進入立法會<br />\n71 #朱凱迪 向外媒講抗爭者「唔係爭取真普選」<br />\n71 #黃碧雲 於facebook上割勇武蓆<br />\n74 #黃碧雲 提倡書面傳閱財委會議案<br />\n76 #何式凝 指責「光復屯門」趕絕大媽舞為性暴力<br />\n711 #張超雄 絕食時無要求四大訴求增加「實行真雙普選」<br />\n714 #朱凱廸 捨身保護警察<br />\n717 #林卓廷 企圖用抗爭者照片威脅要抗爭者停手<br />\n718 #張超雄、#楊岳橋、#尹兆堅 企圖復活逃犯條例修訂<br />\n718 #張超雄 組織老人糾察隊企喺抗爭前線推老人家去死利用老人破壞抗爭<br />\n719 #楊岳橋 指義士流亡影響香港聲譽<br />\n719 #黎志英 頭版披露抗爭者往台灣尋庇護訊息兼開live訪問流亡義士<br />\n725 #民陣 恐嚇市民參與光復元朗或被捕 <br />\n730 #潘小濤 呼籲成立大台統籌物資<br />\n81 #朱凱廸 老作受到恐嚇訊息<br />\n83 #張超雄 上881話成立獨立調查委員會就好多示威者收貨<br />\n84 #許智峯 呼籲聲緩西環嘅街坊翻屋企<br />\n85前 #民陣、#職工盟 恐嚇市民罷工或不受保障<br />\n85 #何式凝 於天水圍呼籲示威者停留導致七十多人被捕<br />\n85 #毛孟靜 不同意塗污國旗(而非表示理解及有保留) 兼指示手下搶劫美國旗，涉違反香港法例第210章 《盜竊罪條例》第10條《搶劫罪》 <br />\n85 #劉細良 叫停「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n86 #李安然 話黑社會打人切勿私了，反而要搵黑警幫手<br />\n86 #梁耀忠 守護深水埗警署玻璃仲叫市民等黑警消息<br />\n89 #譚文豪 恐嚇和你飛市民或會干犯機場附例"},{"pid":"cc58cb75efebbeecc07d00bd60c8d27790a1a1b0","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慎防左膠啊 依條仆街仲要曲解天琦原意 話成場運動要和理非到尾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"2f37351c00feb6160b8a71ad70e97dddd4da564b","tid":1437430,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba8ef071d0e2eda77f6bbb11945dba5ae3f2765d","tid":1437430,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"[極重要!!!!]大埔飲飲食食交通攻略[附自制地圖]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437153</a>"},{"pid":"6abf44f5f406d4cf383f9ca6b8941e8d1d7d4796","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班𤅄民打手除左負皮我仲識啲咩？以為可以呃到連登仔？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a21bf9d5053bd397d5ac87d9bc790434539c285e","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再吹奏條仆街，條仆街諗住自保咋</span></span>"},{"pid":"510df77623785963e86280d4cca2bb99e585ac05","tid":1437430,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T1